{"tid":256042,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"真係好羡慕轉數快嘅人","createTime":"2017-05-24T08:56:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-25T15:35:19.000Z","uid":22136,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bd48e4afd32a697b33207be5f927790155651a5e","tid":256042,"uid":22136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T08:56:53.000Z","msg":"自問又蠢又鈍 講野又唔叻<br />\n成日都講得好快又冇point 講一件事嘅時候好多時人地都聽唔到<br />\n返工又成日比人屌轉數慢 on99咁<br />\n轉數呢樣野係咪天生 定係後天都有得培訓岀嚟<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e344bc0e5ccc58a49864b9df2ae07c875c9a4cc6","tid":256042,"uid":21355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T08:57:30.000Z","msg":"冇咖啦"},{"pid":"c252795dc450e5b3e28a6f9aa3c74efa6fece07d","tid":256042,"uid":22136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T08:58:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5accef99e5557e73b4f0b00753e3333ac9419c18","tid":256042,"uid":72173,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T09:02:08.000Z","msg":"平時諗野好快但講野好易口窒窒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講緊野果時，好難一邊諗要講乜<br />\n<br />\n唔知點解會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddcbcb5be28b5a6532dec6562136cac26d97e1e6","tid":256042,"uid":3232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T09:33:15.000Z","msg":"同樓主一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時講野要load好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c16174f031c023ee9fcddf68304e3dd42da7201","tid":256042,"uid":22136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T11:21:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>平時諗野好快但講野好易口窒窒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講緊野果時，好難一邊諗要講乜<br />\n<br />\n唔知點解會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌一撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一講野就諗唔到野 個腦空左<br />\n就算講之前諗好曬點講 一岀聲就窒下窒下"},{"pid":"fff3082249c4a0a9004f26ce56e32c454c763733","tid":256042,"uid":15823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T11:38:32.000Z","msg":"成日唔講野係咁架喇<br />\n女仔講野多數叻係因為佢地每日都有傾電話既時間"},{"pid":"965f1c5c9d8dc7b39d177e88595f98e447725fc4","tid":256042,"uid":107623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T11:44:36.000Z","msg":"轉數唔快就要熟書。<br />\n熟書用無死"},{"pid":"69d851fbcdeb6149a793d4539194876a7ccc656a","tid":256042,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T11:45:50.000Z","msg":"轉數快同識講嘢係兩回事嚟架喎。<br />\n<br />\n大學有好多教授諗嘢好快，講又講得快，不過一舊一舊，仲會自己駛翻自己啲Point，抄完筆記又要重寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好多女人都識講嘢，不過係90％廢up，外圍打圈、講完等於冇講，又冇中心論點。<br />\n<br />\n利申：日撚日對住啲咁嘅人，好想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef751ca068a4ad59e4b4af73dc537a2c11711e5b","tid":256042,"uid":31896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T11:48:02.000Z","msg":"你試下每日夜晚run番一次今日有啲咩講得快又冇point又亂 然後再組織諗下如果有類似情況再發生點樣表達先好啲<br />\n組織力都係靠練習練番來<br />\n比啲信心盡量冷靜<br />\n<br />\n利申:0組織力"},{"pid":"b9f5cc19ef2e79de2b1ab4b11b6c342e0ce7e544","tid":256042,"uid":69939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T11:48:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同樓主一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時講野要load好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係⋯ 未必唔係好事<br />\n出黎做野 好多時諗清楚先好講⋯<br />\n有同事 因為講野又直又掘 <br />\n得罪唔少人⋯"},{"pid":"dcd18229d875bf1de8bc5e5fce726783bd4a370a","tid":256042,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T11:51:41.000Z","msg":"轉數多數係天生<br />\n口才就可以練"},{"pid":"876bc5588f620ffa2e48edeb1b7b3b356c9023c0","tid":256042,"uid":28092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T12:04:14.000Z","msg":"轉數快但係有時唔知應唔應該講出口先煩"},{"pid":"5bf62e0950a25056feac2b15bf53757e2ae857f5","tid":256042,"uid":57204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T12:09:52.000Z","msg":"你講粗口就叻！"},{"pid":"4ff40cb1879148e156b129aa226e6ea4c0a31902","tid":256042,"uid":28768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T12:47:16.000Z","msg":"細個成日同屋企人鬥咀 初中啲MK朋友成日撩交嗌 我覺得鬧交講粗口係無料先講 之後就成日逼自己一個粗口都唔講同佢地鬧 諗返起想多謝佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9673d356744e511d7e86c8af3a6909c0f31d0905","tid":256042,"uid":22136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T12:55:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成日唔講野係咁架喇<br />\n女仔講野多數叻係因為佢地每日都有傾電話既時間</blockquote><br />\n咁係咪要同人傾多啲電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcab7e454ae8c6cf80233fb8a60eaf74c8ab8003","tid":256042,"uid":65593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T12:58:47.000Z","msg":"轉數快但口臭又有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好少講野 因為成日一開口就串人得罪人"},{"pid":"5bc6de42d060e7feddf4eaf12a885173f9111a6b","tid":256042,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl